Method Detail

getModuleId

public int getModuleId()
Returns this module's instance identifier. The identifier is an integer that is unique within a given session of communications with SBW. Note that module instance identifiers change between sessions with SBW, so a module should never store this value or assume that it will have the same identifier every time.

Returns:
an integer representing the module's identifier
